name: DS Academy
description: DS Academy enables the fortunate among us to contribute to the journey of those who follow close behind. Through interactive workshops, live events, and other professional development tools, DS Academy partners with educational institutions, government agencies, and other non-profits to initiate and support positive change in the business world and the world at large, one inspired young person at a time.

name: The Reserve
description: The Reserve is a multi-sensory shopping experience designed to showcase products and services of entrepreneurs and independent minority and women-owned businesses; providing a fun, inspiring, and interactive experience to all in attendance. Guests will not only have “first-look" opportunities to shop emerging brands but can converse with the entrepreneurs behind them; as well as artists, designers, and other creative professionals who regularly attend the event.

name: I.CON
description: Inspire Conference (I.CON) is a weekend of fun and enrichment where ideas are born, cultivated, and released to effect change in the world. With plenty of opportunities to uplevel your knowledge and interact with peers, executives, and thought leaders, your plan for success will take on new dimensions almost effortlessly.

name: DrivenXP
description: DrivenXP offers brands access to our community of influential millennials and post-millennials, facilitating companies’ ability to provide benefit while they also receive it through our customized experiences. DrivenXP has helped leading brands gain insight through research, create better-tailored content with customer input, and at times simply give back to the world. The right brand narrative is instrumental in creating value for a company, especially when your ideal customers are listening--let DrivenXP open up that channel for your story.
